children.subject: It says "Fall 2019". Is that a typo or is this the wrong form?

history.content:
The Center for Access to Engineering Excellence (CAEE) is looking to hire more CS and EE tutors for the coming semester. You must have gotten a minimum grade of a B in whatever classes you are tutoring for. The position pays $18/hour and you should be able to commit anywhere between 6 to 10 hours per week.

If you are interested please apply below before Sunday.

 https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSe3y2dbk9zymbGPPdEEb8aRicZtMjwjxPCKlBXtJ17bUflYbQ/viewform 

If you any questions, please email Luis Castillo at lecastil@berkeley.edu
